cann health a professional and directtoconsumer health communications network chasedesign a shopper marketing specialist pmkbnc an entertainment and brand agency and craft the networks global adaptation and production arm um media management weber shandwick public relations and futurebrand consultingdesign align with mccann worldgroup to deliver fully integrated solutions fcb is a global fully integrated marketing communications company focused on changing consumer behavior for the benefit of their clients colleagues and communities mullenlowe group is an integrated marketing communications network components include mullenlowe with expertise in brand strategy creative content development and performance analytics mullenlowe profero fullservice integrated digital marketing mullenlowe mediahub media and communications planning and buying and mullenlowe open behaviordriven activation customer relationship management crm and shopper marketingipg mediabrands as the global media arm of ipg is responsible for managing marketing investment for various brands its portfolio encompasses two global fullservice agencies um and initiative which are charged with delivering business results for clients providing strategic counsel and advisory services and navigating the everevolving media landscape rounding out the ipg mediabrands portfolio of services are its specialty business units ansible cadreon magna healix the ipg media lab mediabrands insights rapport reprise and society these agencies focus on media innovation forecasting product development branded content emerging technology mobile search and social and outofhome among others weber shandwick and golin has expertise in area of communication management jack morton is a global brand experience agency and futurebrand is a brand consultancy octagon is a global sports entertainment and lifestyle marketing agency its healthcare communications specialists reside within its global creative networkswithin ian the companys agencies provide an array of global communications and marketing services its digital specialist agencies provide digital capabilities and service their own client rosters while also serving as digital partners in addition its domestic integrated agencies including hill holliday carmichael lynch and tierney provide a range of advertising marketing communications services andor marketing services and partner with its global operating divisions as needed cmg includes weber shandwick cassidy devries golin futurebrand jack morton and octagon worldwide provides clients with diversified services including public relations meeting and event production sports and entertainment marketing corporate and brand identity and strategic marketing consulting » full overview of ipgn company address interpublic group of companies inc 99 rd avenew york   ny    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation michael roth  frank mergenthaler  philippe krakowsky  ellen johnson  christopher carroll  » more officers  directors interpublic group of companies inc news ad company interpublics results disappoint shares slide jul   update ad company interpublics results disappoint shares slide jul   briefreginterpublic announces second quarter and first half  results jul   ad company interpublics revenue slips  pct jul   brieflee wyatt jr joins interpublic board of directors jun   » more ipgn news related topics stocksstock screeneradvertising  marketing ipg stock quote  interpublic group of companies inc the common stock price  nasdaqcom hot topics etfs  smart portfolio  currencies  online broker center search home  quotes  ipg interpublic group of companies inc the common stock quote  summary data ipg        get ipg alerts delayed  data as of aug   9 et    find a broker to begin trading ipg now exchangenyse industry technology community rating view    ipg real time ipg     edit symbol list symbol lookup real time nls trade reporting flashquotes infoquotes summary quote charts i